- Real-time progress tracking with detailed console output
- Separate tracking for rare accounts
- Custom footer with GIF support
- Badge name display in console (readable format)
- Intelligent rate limiting with auto-detection
- Proxy support for enhanced privacy
- Duplicate prevention system

